Private email addresses
=======================

<a id="tails"></a>

tails
-----

For matters that are listed in none of the above and for
vulnerabilities disclosures, you can write encrypted emails to
<tails@boum.org>. See the
[[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#private]].

<a id="tails-accounting"></a>

tails-accounting
-----------------

If you want to fund Tails please write to
<tails-accounting@boum.org>. See the
[[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#accounting]].

<a id="tails-press"></a>

tails-press
-----------

If you're a journalist wanting to write about Tails, or if you want to
send us links to [[press articles|press]] about Tails, please write to
<tails-press@boum.org>. See the
[[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#press]].

<a id="tails-support-private"></a>

tails-support-private
---------------------

You can write encrypted emails to <tails-support-private@boum.org> if
you need help that requires you to send compromising information. See
the [[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#support]].

<a id="tails-sysadmins"></a>

tails-sysadmins
---------------

To talk about our infrastructure (servers, test suite, repositories,
mirrors...) please write to <tails-sysadmins@boum.org>. See the
[[OpenPGP key|doc/about/openpgp_keys#sysadmins]].

IRC channels
============

You can join our [[#tails|support/chat]] and
[[#tails-dev|contribute/chat]] chatrooms; Note: only a few Tails core
developers hang out there, so email is preferred for anything that
might be of interest for the larger Tails development community.
